x4EF6;&#xFF0C;&#x4F7F;&#x7528;&#x4E0B;&#x9762;&#x8FD9;&#x4E2A;&#x547D;&#x4EE4;\n# &#x5728; &lt;layer-dir&gt; &#x4E2D;&#x4E3A; &lt;recipe-name&gt; &#x589E;&#x52A0;&#x9644;&#x52A0;&#x6587;&#x4EF6;\ndevtool\tupdate-recipe\t&lt;recipe-name&gt;\t-a\t&lt;layer-dir&gt;</pre>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"postamble\" class=\"status\">\nLast Updated 2020-06-28 Sun 12:00.<br>Render by <a href=\"https://github.com/CodeFalling/hexo-renderer-org\">hexo-renderer-org</a> with <a href=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/emacs/\">Emacs</a> 26.3 (<a href=\"https://orgmode.org\">Org</a> mode 9.3.7)\n</div>\n"}
